text: Boomerang is a 1934 British drama film directed by Arthur Maude and starring Lester Matthews, Nora Swinburne, and Harvey Braban. It was made at Walton Studios.Wood p.81 ==Cast== * Lester Matthews as David Kennedy * Nora Swinburne as Elizabeth Stafford * Harvey Braban * Wallace Geoffrey * Charles Mortimer * Millicent Wolf ==References== ==Bibliography== * Low, Rachael.
